{"data":[{"date":"09:38 17/06","title":"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-duc-thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-o-tran-gap-can-tho.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u 16/6, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.</h2><h2>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/HLV-Duc-Thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-Bui-Tien-Dung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, thay th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi x\u1ee9 T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng. L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a cho bi\u1ebft: Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan s\u00e1t k\u0129 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Thanh Th\u1eafng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, n\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ngo\u1ea1i binh, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng.\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf chi\u1ec1u cao s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Thanh Th\u1eafng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u00f4m nay Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua cho FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Nh\u00ecn chung h\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng v\u1eabn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 7 v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/6, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018-168-188690.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018-168-188690.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"270","checkdouble":"188698"},{"date":"10:04 17/06","title":"Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/modric-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Croatia, Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng Lionel Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng Iceland</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Iceland nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Argentina l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm, ngay ph\u00fat 19 do c\u00f4ng Sergio Aguero nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb san h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 4 ph\u00fat sau. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 64, Argentina c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly 11m, ng\u00f4i sao Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Iceland. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Argentina d\u00f9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 28 l\u1ea7n (ri\u00eang Messi c\u00f3 17) nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m 1-1 trong ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty, Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Modric \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Argentina s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. H\u1ecd nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nigeria 2-0 nh\u1edd 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: 1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Oghenekaro Etebo, 1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Luka Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hy v\u1ecdng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i cho Croatia nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin, Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng. Anh c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u1ecd khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric an dinh chien thang cho Croatia\" title=\"Modric an dinh chien thang cho Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-croatia-20-nigeria.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Argentina c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</em>\u201d, Modric n\u00f3i sau khi nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-0 Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Argentina. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a d\u00f9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Croatia s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o 1h c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 22 v\u00e0 27 th\u00e1ng 6 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-argentina-bi-iceland-cam-chan-ngay-ra-quan-466-188677.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/aguero-bao-ve-messi-sau-pha-sut-truot-pen-tham-hoa-469-188674.html\">Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau pha s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t pen th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/messi-nhan-loi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-argentina-469-188670.html\">Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"269","checkdouble":"188699"},{"date":"10:09 17/06","title":"HLV Tite ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-tite-dua-thong-bao-bat-ngo-ve-tinh-trang-suc-khoe-cua-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM 17h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM 17h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/TPHCM.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>L\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u cho th\u1ea5y TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i ngon c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u1edf m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh chi\u1ec1u nay, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf V-League 2018 v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 8 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 L\u1ea1ch Tray, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, 8 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (thua 4). V\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n7 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 qua \u1edf V-League 2018, TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i BXH l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u1edf Vinh, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 3. V\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a L\u1ea1ch Tray, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League.<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u2013 V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ho\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Anh H\u00f9ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, Th\u00e0nh Long, \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o, Stevens, Fagan.<br>\r\n+ TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh: Thanh Di\u1ec7p \u2013 \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n Robert, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u1eefu Tu\u1ea5n, Tavares, Phi S\u01a1n, V\u0103n Thu\u1eadn, Marronkle, Hu\u1ef3nh Kesley, Quang Nam.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"268","checkdouble":"188700"},{"date":"10:15 17/06","title":"Nh\u00e2\u0323n \u0111i\u0323nh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 17h00 nga\u0300y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/