 font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Ngay sau khi giai \u0111oa\u0323n l\u01b0\u01a1\u0323t \u0111i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, BTC V-League 2018 quy\u00ea\u0301t \u0111i\u0323nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c lu\u00f4n giai do\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5y n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2m \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m vo\u0300ng 14 co\u0301 le\u0303 la\u0300 cu\u00f4\u0323c so ta\u0300i gi\u01b0\u0303a 2 \u0111\u00f4\u0323i thu\u1ed9c khu v\u1ef1c Duy\u00ean h\u1ea3i Nam Trung B\u1ed9. Hi\u00ea\u0323n ta\u0323i, tinh th\u00e2\u0300n thi \u0111\u00e2\u0301u cu\u0309a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u00e2\u0301t cao. Sau ma\u0323ch 6 tr\u00e2\u0323n li\u00ean ti\u00ea\u0301p kh\u00f4ng th\u0103\u0301ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n \u0111a\u0303 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u0103\u0300ng vi\u00ea\u0323c \u0111a\u0301nh ba\u0323i Bi\u0300nh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (3-0) va\u0300 C\u00e2\u0300n Th\u01a1 (2-1) \u01a1\u0309 2 vo\u0300ng \u0111\u00e2\u0301u g\u00e2\u0300n nh\u00e2\u0301t. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \"ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0300i \u0111o\u0301ng th\u00ea\u0301\" Tru\u0300m Ti\u0309nh (thay L\u00e2m Ti Ph\u00f4ng nh\u00e2\u0323n a\u0301n treo gio\u0300) \u0111a\u0303 to\u0309a sa\u0301ng v\u01a1\u0301i 3 ba\u0300n th\u0103\u0301ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u00ea\u0323c gia\u0300nh \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c 6 \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m \u01a1\u0309 2 vo\u0300ng \u0111\u00e2\u0301u cu\u00f4\u0301i giai \u0111oa\u0323n l\u01b0\u01a1\u0323t \u0111i \u0111a\u0303 giu\u0301p ca\u0301c c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 Sanna Kha\u0301nh Ho\u0300a v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean vi\u0323 tri\u0301 th\u01b0\u0301 3 tr\u00ean BXH v\u01a1\u0301i 20 \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m. \u0110\u00e2y co\u0301 th\u00ea\u0309 coi la\u0300 tha\u0300nh c\u00f4ng ngoa\u0300i mong \u0111\u01a1\u0323i \u0111\u00f4\u0301i v\u01a1\u0301i \u0111oa\u0300n qu\u00e2n cu\u0309a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n va\u0300 ch\u0103\u0301c ch\u0103\u0301n se\u0303 ti\u00ea\u0301p th\u00eam nhi\u00ea\u0300u t\u01b0\u0323 tin cho \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng ph\u00f4\u0301 bi\u00ea\u0309n trong giai \u0111oa\u0323n l\u01b0\u01a1\u0323t v\u00ea\u0300.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u00ea\u0301n tuy\u00ea\u0301n, tuy \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111i\u0323ch V-League, nh\u01b0ng Qua\u0309ng Nam ch\u01b0a th\u00ea\u0309 hi\u00ea\u0323n \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 trong su\u00f4\u0301t giai \u0111oa\u0323n l\u01b0\u01a1\u0323t \u0111i v\u1eeba qua. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00e2\u0300y tro\u0300 HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111a\u0303 xu\u00e2\u0301t s\u0103\u0301c ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c do\u0300ng \u0111a\u0301nh ba\u0323i chu\u0309 nha\u0300 Hoa\u0300ng Anh Gia Lai 3-2 nh\u01a1\u0300 2 ba\u0300n v\u00e0o 10 phu\u0301t cu\u00f4\u0301i tr\u00e2\u0323n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 14, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 v\u01a1\u0301i 19 \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m, chi\u0309 ke\u0301m chi\u0301nh \u0111\u00f4\u0301i thu\u0309 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 1 \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua\u0309ng Nam ch\u0103\u0301c ch\u0103\u0301n se\u0303 \u0111\u0103\u0323t nhi\u00ea\u0300u quy\u00ea\u0301t t\u00e2m trong chuy\u00ea\u0301n ha\u0300nh qu\u00e2n t\u01a1\u0301i Nha Trang chi\u1ec1u n\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 nhi\u00ea\u0323m vu\u0323 kh\u00f4ng h\u00ea\u0300 d\u00ea\u0303 da\u0300ng. N\u00ean nh\u01a1\u0301 r\u0103\u0300ng phong \u0111\u00f4\u0323 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch cu\u0309a Qua\u0309ng Nam la\u0300 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u0323c s\u01b0\u0323 t\u00f4\u0301t, khi chi\u0309 co\u0301 2 chi\u00ea\u0301n th\u0103\u0301ng sau 6 tr\u00e2\u0323n \u0111a\u0303 qua (Thua 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMo\u0323i chuy\u00ea\u0323n ca\u0300ng tr\u01a1\u0309 n\u00ean kho\u0301 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00f4\u0301i v\u01a1\u0301i Qua\u0309ng Nam, khi tr\u00e2\u0323n na\u0300y ho\u0323 thi\u00ea\u0301u v\u0103\u0301ng hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Claudecir v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00ea\u0300u do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin l\u01b0\u0323c l\u01b0\u01a1\u0323ng<br>\r\nSanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: Claudecir v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nSanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, Tr\u1ecdng B\u00ecnh, \u0110\u00ecnh Kh\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed, Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Nh\u01a1n, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Toure, Trung Hi\u1ebfu, Duy Thanh, Zarour.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng, Huy H\u00f9ng, Rosa, V\u0103n H\u00e0, Thanh H\u01b0ng, Quang Huy, \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1eafng, Thanh Trung, Thiago, T\u1ea5n Sinh, V\u0103n H\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTSBT - H\u01a1n 2,5 ba\u0300n th\u0103\u0301ng: Nh\u01b0\u0303ng tr\u00e2\u0323n \u0111\u00e2\u0301u co\u0301 s\u01b0\u0323 go\u0301p m\u0103\u0323t qua\u0309 Qua\u0309ng Nam lu\u00f4n mang \u0111\u00ea\u0301n cho NHM b\u01b0\u0303a ti\u00ea\u0323c ba\u0300n th\u0103\u0301ng thi\u0323nh soa\u0323n. Chi\u00ea\u0301n th\u0103\u0301ng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0301c Hoa\u0300ng Anh Gia Lai la\u0300 m\u00f4\u0323t trong s\u00f4\u0301 nh\u01b0\u0303ng b\u01b0\u0303a ti\u00ea\u0323c \u0111o\u0301. Th\u00f4\u0301ng k\u00ea cho th\u00e2\u0301y, 5/7 tr\u00e2\u0323n xa nha\u0300 g\u00e2\u0300n \u0111\u00e2y cu\u0309a \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng x\u01b0\u0301 Qua\u0309ng \u0111\u00ea\u0300u xu\u00e2\u0301t hi\u00ea\u0323n i\u0301t nh\u00e2\u0301t 3 ba\u0300n th\u0103\u0301ng. B\u00ean kia chi\u00ea\u0301n tuy\u00ea\u0301n, 5 tr\u00e2\u0323n g\u00e2\u0300n nh\u00e2\u0301t cu\u0309a Sanna Kha\u0301nh Ho\u0300a cu\u0303ng \u0111\u00ea\u0300u co\u0301 t\u01b0\u0300 3 ba\u0300n th\u0103\u0301ng tr\u01a1\u0309 l\u00ean.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"267","checkdouble":"188702"},{"date":"10:38 17/06","title":"Nh\u00ecn g\u01b0\u01a1ng Argentina, HLV \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c e d\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhin-guong-argentina-hlv-dt-duc-phat-bieu-than-trong-truoc-tran-gap-mexico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><h2>HLV \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c e d\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i nay (gi\u1edd VN). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i cho \u2018nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c\u2019. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico HLV \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c e d\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico HLV \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c e d\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/nhin-guong-argentina-hlv-dt-duc-phat-bieu-than-trong-truoc-tran-gap-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Joachim Loew t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng\u00a0kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. B\u1ea1n h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u0103ng n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Khi \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup r\u1ed3i th\u00ec m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Loew t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan d\u00f9 \u00f4ng v\u1eabn tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fa v\u1ecb. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t\", \u00f4ng Loew n\u00f3i th\u00eam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. M\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e9 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil, \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc-421-188694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc-421-188694.html\">HLV Mexico tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 17/6, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Mexico \u00f4ng Juan Carlos Osorio \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-tai-world-cup-2018-co-xe-tang-dang-so-cua-joachim-low-466-188065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/dt-duc-tai-world-cup-2018-co-xe-tang-dang-so-cua-joachim-low.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-tai-world-cup-2018-co-xe-tang-dang-so-cua-joachim-low-466-188065.html\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Joachim Low</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u201cC\u1ed7 xe...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua-462-188692.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua-462-188692.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico (22h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngai v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mexico, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y c\u00fap.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"266","checkdouble":"188703"},{"date":"10:45 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM 17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/TPHCM.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM 17h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM 17h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/TPHCM.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs TPHCM: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>L\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u cho th\u1ea5y TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i ngon c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u1edf m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh chi\u1ec1u nay, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf V-League 2018 v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 8 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 L\u1ea1ch Tray, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, 8 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (thua 4). V\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n7 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 qua \u1edf V-League 2018, TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i BXH l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u1edf Vinh, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 3. V\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a L\u1ea1ch Tray, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League.<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u2013 V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ho\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Anh H\u00f9ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, Th\u00e0nh Long, \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o, Stevens, Fagan.<br>\r\n+ TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh: Thanh Di\u1ec7p \u2013 \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n Robert, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u1eefu Tu\u1ea5n, Tavares, Phi S\u01a1n, V\u0103n Thu\u1eadn, Marronkle, Hu\u1ef3nh Kesley, Quang Nam.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"265","checkdouble":"188704"},{"date":"11:10 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA 17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-binh-duong-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA 17h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA 17h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/tong-hop-slna-51-binh-duong-luot-ve-chung-ket-cup-qg-2017.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m t\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u nay, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 SLNA, CLB \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00ean. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi k\u00e9o d\u00e0i b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Vinh. C\u00f2n chi\u1ec1u nay, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00ean nh\u1edb, \u1edf V-League 2018, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu (th\u1eafng 4). Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, SLNA l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a (h\u00f2a 3, thua 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n ngay c\u1ea3 khi h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA trong 6 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (h\u00f2a 4, thua 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- SLNA b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 6 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 4).<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 4 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nhau v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a SLNA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: \u0110\u1ee9c C\u01b0\u1eddng \u2013 Xu\u00e2n Lu\u00e2n, Ng\u1ecdc M\u1ea1nh, Tanidis, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Kortzorg, Tr\u1ecdng Huy, V\u0103n V\u0169, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n+ SLNA: V\u0169 H\u1ea3i \u2013 Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, M\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, S\u1ef9 S\u00e2m, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n, Osmar, Olaha.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"264","checkdouble":"188705"},{"date":"11:17 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-mexico-du-doan-duc-vs-mexico-va-soi-keo-duc-vs-mexico.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 nghi ng\u1edd n\u00e0o d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. L\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn l\u00e0m r\u00f5 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 22h ng\u00e0y 17/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Luzhniki (Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> \u0110\u1ee9c -0.98*0:1 1/4*0.88 Mexico<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.99*2 3/4*0.93 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-mexico-du-doan-duc-vs-mexico-va-soi-keo-duc-vs-mexico.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico 22h ng\u00e0y 17/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nghi ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c Die Mannschaft c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Saudi Arabia 2-1 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 xoa d\u1ecbu d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Joachim Low.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Low va hoc tro\" title=\"Duc Low va hoc tro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Duc-Low-va-hoc-tro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. L\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Confed Cup 2017, h\u1ecd h\u00f2a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 \u1edf 1 trong 2 tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Euro 2016, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thua Slovakia 1-3 v\u00e0 th\u1eafng Hungary 2-0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Low \u0111\u00e1 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u00ec h\u00f2a t\u1edbi 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan v\u00e0 Cameroon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta r\u00fat ra m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u: Chu\u1ed7i giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u01b0ng b\u00edt nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u1eeba qua, Low nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i (Leroy Sane ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc bo roi Sane\" title=\"Duc bo roi Sane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/hummels-phat-bieu-ve-sane-va-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ebfn Sane c\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n song \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa. N\u00f3 kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n khi v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may cho Mexico khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u201cXe t\u0103ng\u201d \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00e2m tr\u1eadn. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Mexico. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n 60%, tung ra 25 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee7 lo\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1ee9c. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 0 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 khoa h\u1ecdc, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Mexico nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u1ed3n. Chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 4-1 sau 12 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio cua Mexico phat bieu day tu tin truoc tran gap nha DKVD DT Duc\" title=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio c\u1ee7a Mexico ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mexico c\u1ee7a HLV\u00a0Osorio mong manh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Mexico nh\u00ecn chung r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0o gi\u1edd kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p: 22h ng\u00e0y 17/6 theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, El Tri b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 mong manh. T\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 5 tr\u1eadn th\u00ec l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 10 b\u00e0n, t\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh 2 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Juan Osorio t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Mexico s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t. Sau kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec1 cao s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng, t\u00ednh to\u00e1n, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n xem nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc-421-188694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-tuyen-bo-day-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-dt-duc-421-188694.html\">HLV Mexico tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 17/6, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Mexico \u00f4ng Juan Carlos Osorio \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Mexico, h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f2 h\u1ecd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t khu\u00f4n kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u0169 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 9 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u1eeb khi Miroslav Klose chia tay, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Timo Werner h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd th\u1ebf vai l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n ghi 21 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho RB Leipzig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Timo Werner tai DT Duc\" title=\"Timo Werner tai DT Duc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/werner-phat-bieu-ve-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Werner mang th\u00eam ni\u1ec1m tin cho \u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, Werner ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 14 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o. T\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017 c\u0169ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n c\u1ed9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Thomas Muller th\u00ednh nh\u1ea1y, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n Toni Kroos, Julian Draxler hay Mesut Ozil\u2026 r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh cho m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed1c 3 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u1ec9 ti\u00eau \u201cOver\u201d m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7t ra s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5.<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 (O 10)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 qu\u1ea3 (-1 3/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 3 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u0111a (U 3)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Mexico nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1 th\u1ebb<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u00ednh:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- <strong>\u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t </strong>(-1 1/4)<br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng </strong>(O 2 3/4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"263","checkdouble":"188706"},{"date":"11:30 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-nam-dinh-vs-quang-ninh-18h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 176 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-bong-da-quang-ninh-vs-nam-dinh-18h00-21-4-vong-6-v-league-2018-rs650.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>V\u00f2ng cu\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League (v\u00f2ng 13), Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng quen thu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong d\u00f9 sao h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y, \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ch\u00ed t\u1eed c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngo\u1ea1i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft d\u1ecbnh thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Benjamin \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n d\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 t\u00ean Antonio. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi v\u1eady, ngay c\u1ea3 khi Antonio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ecbp \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c xa x\u00f4i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ed1i nay c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 thua tan t\u00e1c 1-4 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch. Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c th\u1eadt s\u1ef1, \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3. V\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch s\u00e1ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nNam \u0110\u1ecbnh: Minh Nh\u1ef1t; V\u0103n Qu\u00fd, Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, H\u1eefu Qu\u00fd, H\u1ea1 Long, V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0110\u1ee9c Nam, Ng\u1ecdc Nam, S\u1ef9 Minh, Henry, Minh Tu\u1ea5n.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh: Tu\u1ea5n Linh, V\u0103n Khoa, Thanh H\u00e0o, Hoa H\u00f9ng, H\u1ea3i Huy, M\u1ea1c Qu\u00e2n, Huy C\u01b0\u1eddng, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, Nguy\u00ean Sa, Vinicius, Edyson.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"262","checkdouble":"188707"},{"date":"11:48 17/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 17/6: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o t\u1eadp, Salah xem ra v\u1eabn ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/ngay-hom-nay-176.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (17/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o t\u1eadp, Salah xem ra v\u1eabn ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/anh4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nTheo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi ghi nh\u1eadn, Mohamed Salah ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a 3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o t\u1eadp v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c m\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o t\u1eadp t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng ri\u00eang v\u1edbi Salah v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f9ng vai. Anh t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u1ebfn Nga, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho r\u1eb1ng vai tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Salah v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Salah \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n s\u00e2n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 26 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2n t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Hector Cuper v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng A m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\r\n<h2>HLV Tite: 'Neymar v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng'</h2>\r\nHLV Tite c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil cho bi\u1ebft Neymar v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain b\u1ecb r\u1ea1n x\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 bong g\u00e2n m\u1eaft c\u00e1. D\u00f9 HLV Tite tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, Neymar kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tite-dua-thong-bao-bat-ngo-ve-tinh-trang-suc-khoe-cua-neymar-421-188700.html\">HLV Tite ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Maradona b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Argentina</h2>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \"Albiceleste\" b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \"c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng\" v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c khi d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/maradona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CLB Napoli \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Jacqui Oatley c\u1ee7a BBC, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a tin tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Maradona l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOatley cho bi\u1ebft: \"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t l\u00ean 'Diego' v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi, d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n gi\u00f3 v\u00e0 v\u1eaby tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t quay \u0111i trong m\u1ed9t c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng\".\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vua-bong-da-maradona-bi-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-o-tran-argentina-vs-iceland-421-188701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/vua-bong-da-maradona-bi-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-o-tran-argentina-vs-iceland.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vua-bong-da-maradona-bi-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-o-tran-argentina-vs-iceland-421-188701.html\">Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland</span><br>\r\n<span>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Albiceleste b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c khi d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iceland</h2>\r\nJavier Mascherano cho r\u1eb1ng Argentina g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 v\u00ec Iceland ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c. \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u\", Mascherano cho bi\u1ebft.\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nigeria t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn</h2>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Nigeria \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t gi\u1eadn d\u1eef sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \"\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\" g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h2>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Youssef Msakni c\u1ee7a Tunisia coi nh\u1eb9 \"Tam s\u01b0\". Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c\". Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 19/6.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"261","checkdouble":"188708"},{"date":"07:04 17/06","title":"Mourinho v\u1ebd ra k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/mourinho-ve-ra-kich-ban-khong-tuong-cho-ronaldo-va-messi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Argentina, v\u1edbi Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u2026</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i ri\u00eang l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nam M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-3</span> k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u1edd c\u00fa hat-trick si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a CR7, trong khi Argentina b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecb t\u00e2n binh Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1 v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh M10 s\u1eafm vai t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u1edf qu\u1ea3 penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-ve-ra-kich-ban-khong-tuong-cho-ronaldo-va-messi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Ronaldo \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi th\u1eafng th\u1ebf Messi \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong khi ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng vinh quang ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i. Tuy nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a CR7, c\u1ea3 hai r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft trong m\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 theo d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Man Utd, Argentina c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C r\u1ed3i l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt c\u1ea3n bao g\u1ed3m Australia, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2014. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng B s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Brazil<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd c\u00f2n v\u1ebd ra vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ec9nh cao m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t Mourinho:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cHai c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Brazil v\u00e0 Argentina vs \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn theo c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u \u00e1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2014 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1eefa, v\u1eady n\u00ean Brazil s\u1ebd th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Argentina s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc qua th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, v\u1edbi Ronaldo vs Messi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho c\u00e1c anh t\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng!\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo!</span><br>\r\nBa b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng Sochi, Cristiano Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"260","checkdouble":"188683"},{"date":"07:20 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Yao Hermann Kouassi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eeba chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y sau 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Thai-League.</h2><h2>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Thai-League,\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yao Hermann Kouassi</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/shb-da-nang-trinh-hang-thaileague-o-tran-gap-hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p  HAGL?. \u1ea2nh: Bongda.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Thai-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 Yao Hermann Kouassi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kouassi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u00e1i Lan. Anh t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Thai Division League (Thai-League 2) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Thai-League 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Chiangmai, Bangkok v\u00e0 Samut Sakhon.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m67 nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i Kouassi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 61 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 136 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Kouassi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd san s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng c\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo v\u00e0 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Diogo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (ITC) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n HAGL v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"259","checkdouble":"188684"},{"date":"07:51 17/06","title":"B\u1ecb c\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/hagl-that-chat-ky-luat-mua-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t m\u00f9a World Cup nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9c khuya xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.</h2><h2>HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG V-League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba chung vui xem World Cup v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t CLB HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u201cthi\u1ebft qu\u00e2n lu\u1eadt\u201d trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HAGL c\u1ea5m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9c khuya xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn theo khu\u00f4n ph\u00e9p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/HAGL-that-chat-ky-luat-mua-World-Cup-2018--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m th\u1ee9c khuya xem World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL cho bi\u1ebft BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xem nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafng nghe nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c em \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn s\u1edbm, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o h\u00f4m sau\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i, song to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c t\u1ea1i V.League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cC\u00e1c em c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c r\u00f5 t\u1eadp trung cho V-League m\u1edbi l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng, xem World Cup c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ecdn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y, l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9, n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e0nh kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n xem World Cup. Do \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn s\u1edbm l\u00fac 7 gi\u1edd, 8 gi\u1edd t\u1ed1i th\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung xem c\u00f9ng nhau, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 xem c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang lu\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng. CLB kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 vi ph\u1ea1m CLB s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u1ec9 lu\u1eadt n\u1eb7ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb7t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u00fd th\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ea1i H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n. \u1ede 3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n, v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"258","checkdouble":"188685"},{"date":"07:53 17/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (17/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1762018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 17/